text: Kelly Louise Morrison (born February 2, 1969) is an American physician and politician who is the member of the U.S. House of Representatives for Minnesota's 3rd congressional district since 2025. Morrison was a member of the Minnesota Senate from 2023 to 2024. She is a member of the Minnesota Democratic–Farmer–Labor Party. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official House of Representatives website * Official campaign website Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Minnesota Category:Politicians from Minneapolis Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:American physicians
